vim: ft=markdown

 - Git supports an `encoding` header in commit messages
   iso8859-13 ok, gb18030 ok, iso-2022-jp ok
   software:
    - GitHub ignores header, tries utf-8, fallbacks to iso8859-1
    - GitHub for Windows always uses utf-8, shows "invalid char" for iso8859
    - giggle 0.7 ok
    - git ok, tig 1.1 ok, gitk ok
    - gitg 0.2.5 segfaults with -O2, same as GitHub otherwise
    - qgit 2.3 same as GitHub
